si_contact_institution: University of Twente, Enschede, The Netherlands
si_remarks: The sitet had a well-developed understory and contained 72 species; the six dominant tree species Abarahamia ditimena, Brachulaena ramiflora, Cryptocaria sp., Ocotea samsosa, Eugenia spp., and Laptolaena together comprised 35% of overall stem density.
